
'''Book: Stakeholder Participation in Sociotechnical Systems Design and Decision-making. By Ali Mostashari. Conceptual Advances, 2005.'''

URL = http://www.lulu.com/content/161418


=Description=

"This book emphasizes the role of effective involvement of stakeholders in the decision-making process for sociotechnical systems from the problem definition stage through implementation. It uses advanced concepts from engineering systems, scientific communication, linguistics and alternative dispute resolution to provide a unified stakeholder-assisted modeling and policy design process for sociotechnical systems such as energy facilities, urban and regional transportation systems, toxic materials siting and other technical systems embedded in a complex social settig. The Cape Wind offshore wind energy project is used as an illustrative case study of the stakeholder process."
(http://www.lulu.com/content/161418)


